  <title>Design for testability in JavaFX</title>
  <section xml:id="naming-components-2">
    <title>Naming components</title>
    <para>
      Although components can be located in the AUT even when they
      are not named by the developers, naming components is
      nevertheless a good idea. You can improve the testability of
      your application by using the following method in your JavaFX
      code for the current component class:
      <emphasis>setId();</emphasis>.
    </para>
